Package jx.classfile.datatypes

Class BasicTypeDescriptor

java.lang.Object
jx.classfile.datatypes.BasicTypeDescriptor
public class BasicTypeDescriptor extends Object
This class is used to parse the type descriptor strings for field and method types.
